      "text": "For the-- for the-- for the [NON-ENGLISH], for the village.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 241,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's why they feed him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 241,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had been sitting in place with a little girl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 242,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in Krasnodar.",
